This paper deals with image and video compression and optimization, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The paper also discusses the use of a degradation operator, which is related to information theory (cs.IT). Additionally, the paper addresses the issue of motion blur, which is a topic in graphics (cs.GR).
